   About Us
   Information about the Office of System Safety. GAIN
   The Global Aviation Information Network promotes and facilitates the
   voluntary collection and sharing of aviation safety information
   worldwide.
   Domestic Aviation Safety Data
   Access frequently used aviation safety databases.
     World Aircraft Accident Summary
   The World Aircraft Accident Summary provides access to a condensed
   global summary of all known accidents (domestic and international)
   involving passenger fatalities.
   Safety Reports
   Special studies and statistical reports.
     Safety Risk Management
   Comprehensive approach to assure that systems and techniques have
   safety designed in from the outset.
   Publications
   View and order some safety promotion products.


